For the installation (you can see https://spacy.io/usage), Python and pip is required.

Commands for installation on windows based on the accuracy:

pip install -U pip setuptools wheel
pip install -U spacy
python -m spacy download en_core_web_trf
python -m spacy download el_core_news_lg

(for dispacy visualization (e.g displacy.serve(doc, style="ent")), the server provided is localhost:5000)
